    "description": "JWA is an action packed <strong>diverse </strong> open-world 2.5D <strong>action-adventure RPG</strong>. Play as Jaki, a powerful &amp; clever ninja fox. Wield your shuriken with deadly accuracy as you dodge enemy fire, avoid lethal hazards &amp; defeat clever enemies. The farther North you travel, the more deadly &amp; crafty your enemies become. Craft powerful potions to improve your odds of survival. Help the local residents – maybe a troll with a pink sock or a yogi with a goat named Nibbler. There is always something quirky, challenging &amp; fun to do in Harmony Haven!<br><br>Harmony Haven is full of surprises &amp; Easter eggs for you to discover. Branched dialogue &amp; optional side quests provide interesting choices as you explore strange lands. Start in Eureka, a town full of scientists. Travel to Toon-Town where your skills as a CSI are needed to catch a killer. If you are brave enough, head North to Chillgrave Keep where you match wits with a clever boss. <br><br>Can you become the most powerful ninja in the land? Beat your best score to find out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><strong>Solve Puzzles, Explore Hidden Areas</strong><br>Oh No! You fell through a magical portal &amp; now you are trapped.<br>Are you clever enough to escape?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a05b0090efb41ae543a6ca5eecced6a1.poster.avif?t=1725660818\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a05b0090efb41ae543a6ca5eecced6a1.webm?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a05b0090efb41ae543a6ca5eecced6a1.mp4?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle Bugs, Beasts &amp; Robots to Become the Best Ninja in the Land!</strong><br>On your journey, encounter numerous powerful &amp; tricky enemies.  Wield unique shuriken with deadly accuracy as you dodge enemy fire, avoid lethal hazards &amp; improve your ninja skills. Can you beat your best score &amp; become the best ninja in the land?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a9c8347dbc0de7c780e598c96128fd74.poster.avif?t=1725660818\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a9c8347dbc0de7c780e598c96128fd74.webm?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/a9c8347dbc0de7c780e598c96128fd74.mp4?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/7aac634b0702a2d61eab6d889563296e.poster.avif?t=1725660818\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/7aac634b0702a2d61eab6d889563296e.webm?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/7aac634b0702a2d61eab6d889563296e.mp4?t=1725660818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Discover Rare Items &amp; Improve Your Skills</strong><br>Explore hidden areas &amp; discover valuable rare items that level up your skills. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/b4f32449aa12c942c75e560c710104cd.avif?t=1725660818\" width=624 height=400 /></span><br><br><strong>Craft powerful potions!</strong><br>Collect plants &amp; powerful crystals. Apply crafted potions to ninja stars to increase damage or freeze enemies. Health potions restore health or make you invincible. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/e75916b99528b5f6fd56895d8c0a0d9e.avif?t=1725660818\" width=652 height=366 /></span><br><br><strong>Meet interesting characters!</strong><br>Along your journey, you meet interesting characters. Meet eccentric scientists, like Einstein in Eureka. Or, meet cute lovable characters in Toon Town. Choose to help them with their problems and receive valuable resources which improve your chances of success.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/9c33cabe66cc332479a8bb75c863d2e4.avif?t=1725660818\" width=652 height=366 /></span><br><br><strong>Explore Strange Lands</strong><br>Many adventures, challenges, and quests await Jaki in the open world of Harmony Haven. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808870/extras/0c7518f1ba2655fa17540abfb194fbf2.avif?t=1725660818\" width=652 height=366 /></span><br><br><strong>Manage Your Resources</strong><br>You may buy &amp; sell resources IF you can stand Y-Lee Weasel's prices. Or collect and craft items that improve your skills, enhance your health, or increase damage. Some powerful potions are rare, so use them strategically.",
